<manpage>
    <sample url="sdk\operating_system\crt\libc\stdlib\_ultoa">_ultoa</sample>
    <title> _ultoa, _ultow</title>
    <volume>C 运行库函数</volume>
    <routine_idx> slib_idx.htm </routine_idx>

    <description>
        <para>把无符号长整型数转换为字符串。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>char*</return_val>
        <func_name>_ultoa</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>unsigned long</param_type>
                <param_name>value</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>待转换的无符号长整型数</para>
                </param_note>
            </func_param>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>char*</param_type>
                <param_name>string</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>转换后得到的字符串</para>
                </param_note>
            </func_param>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>int</param_type>
                <param_name>radix</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>value的基数</para>
                </param_note>
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>wchar_t*</return_val>
        <func_name>_ultow</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>unsigned long</param_type>
                <param_name>value</param_name>
            </func_param>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>wchar_t*</param_type>
                <param_name>string</param_name>
            </func_param>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>int</param_type>
                <param_name>radix</param_name>
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

    <return>
        <para>每个函数都返回指向字符串的指针。无错误返回。</para>
    </return>

    <remarks>
        <para>_ultoa函数将value转换为以NULL结尾的字符串，存放在string中（最大33个字节数）。不执行溢出检查。radix指定value的基数；radix的取值范围必须在2 C 36之间。_ultow是_ultoa的宽字符版本。</para>
    </remarks>

    <requirements>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>_ultoa</routine_name>
            <headerfile>stdlib.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>_ultow</routine_name>
            <headerfile>stdlib.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
    </requirements>

    <example>
<pre>
//==========================================================================
// Copyright (c) 2000-2004,  Elastos, Inc.  All Rights Reserved.
//==========================================================================

/* _ultoa.cpp:this program convert ul whose type is unsigned long to string
 */

#include &lt;stdlib.h&gt;
#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;

int main()
{
    char buffer[20];
    unsigned long ul = 1234567890UL;

    _ultoa(ul, buffer, 16);
    printf(&quot;String of unsigned long %lu (radix 16): 0x%s.\n&quot;, ul,
                                                                     buffer);
    return 0;
}
</pre>
    </example>
<result>
String of unsigned long 1234567890 (radix 16): 0x499602d2.
</result>

   

